name: Remembering Newtown
description: Stretch bracelet handcrafted with white and light green Swarovski pearls, rhinestone rondelles, and a pewter awareness ribbon. Swarovski Pearls are simulated pearls made in Wattens, Austria. At the heart of every pearl is an Austrian crystal core. A unique coating by Swarovski gives the pearl it's luminous pearl essence and creates a lustrous shimmer. Handcrafted with pride in remembrance of the innocent lives lost in the Newtown tragedy. Approximately 7.5".
